u1::a "IF YOU WRITE IN ALL CAPS, YOU WILL BE REMINDED OF THE NOTE LATER!" ::?tec
u2::a Mostly you just write notes ::?tec
u3::a "Other symbols can be defined with your own meanings, like >\"special meanings\"" ::?tec
u4::a The >ditto symbol of inverted commas has a special meaning ::?tec
